{"tid":516097,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇接觸過非主流極端類型丶邊緣音樂?","createTime":"2018-01-01T05:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T16:08:43.000Z","uid":18998,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9f48ee195390797b8f5a31e381f86e89a197fdfd","tid":516097,"uid":18998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"講緊嘅唔係hardcore或者metal,<br />\n<br />\n亦唔係Jazz丶Funk呀Remix 果類,<br />\n<br />\n咁我當然都唔係講緊印象派二十世紀音樂嗰啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次想講嘅點係一啲異類音樂,被稱為:<br />\n<br />\n<strong>OUT-OF-THE-ORDINARY, EXTRA-SENSORY MUSIC</strong><br />\n<br />\n相信到而家你都唔知道我講乜,直接去片啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QFwo57WKwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6QFwo57WKwg&d=onFCXyfToMO2LbA4U7NzPgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=b4d60fe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QFwo57WKwg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WFuWPhlsyEI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWFuWPhlsyEI&d=onFCXyfToMO2LbA4U7NzPgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=14081916\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WFuWPhlsyEI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n略略介紹一個外國嘅youtube channel(以下條link)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHkWT_RtOhfZkvLIgHAZJMQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCHkWT_RtOhfZkvLIgHAZJMQ&d=onFCXyfToMO2LbA4U7NzPgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=3ec2692b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHkWT_RtOhfZkvLIgHAZJMQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以聽到入面所有歌都係用好多電子元素syn pad atmosphere echo sound,<br />\n<br />\n但係其實睇完都唔知佢地想做啲乜,<br />\n<br />\n我自己都唔係好了解呢類型音樂到底想點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能呢個亦都係佢地想做嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最有趣嘅地方係呢個Channel會將呢啲音樂同一啲Art work/ 奇怪嘅片帶埋一齊,<br />\n<br />\n成件事就會變得更加光怪陸離,<br />\n<br />\n我相信係香港應該好少人聽,<br />\n<br />\n但是如果有興趣嘅朋友不妨一齊討論一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外我自己都有仿效呢啲音樂做咗小小作品出來,<br />\n係咁意聽下就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ok_GRn8LH9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dok_GRn8LH9A&d=onFCXyfToMO2LbA4U7NzPgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=61ed53ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ok_GRn8LH9A</a>"},{"pid":"114fdfde2e76c4865d00f87aec6f37e0d2d70cb1","tid":516097,"uid":96117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"有無聽過m83 tycho個d"},{"pid":"a844cbfa85dbe614f8d45b36c60f0106c17fdc51","tid":516097,"uid":18998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"114fdfde2e76c4865d00f87aec6f37e0d2d70cb1","tid":516097,"uid":96117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"有無聽過m83 tycho個d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T05:35:59.000Z","msg":"Midnight City 呢啲好出名我都有聽過,<br />\n有冇咩介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f060acfefac4c9b677f5316d0d8b0390256bd94a","tid":516097,"uid":104446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T05:38:48.000Z","msg":"幾得意"},{"pid":"c13eed16988ccffb725cd441a770b08a8bafdcfe","tid":516097,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64e264559282c37344965e694330d8d5399118f5","tid":516097,"uid":18998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T06:58:20.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"f20eef37fbbf417c267eeddf901c0a0d9cd4d327","tid":516097,"uid":158933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T08:23:52.000Z","msg":"佢地個mv都幾有趣"},{"pid":"3b1f802f571b147e099e60203c459d04c69c3e5